<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="si">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI පොඩ්ඩා - AI Video Course</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Sinhala:wght@400;700;900&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #0066ff;
            --deep-blue: #003d99;
            --neon-blue: #00d4ff;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Sinhala', 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: #0a0e27;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Animated Background */
        .bg-video-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .bg-video {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.15;
        }
        
        .gradient-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 20, 60, 0.8) 100%);
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        /* Glassmorphism */
        .glass {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .glass-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        /* Animations */
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        @keyframes glow {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.8), 0 0 60px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.6); }
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse-ring {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0; }
        }
        
        .float-anim { animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
        .glow-anim { animation: glow 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
        
        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0a0e27; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--primary-blue); border-radius: 4px; }
        
        /* Social Icons */
        .social-icon {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .social-icon:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(5deg);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px currentColor);
        }
        
        .social-icon::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -5px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: currentColor;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .social-icon:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.2;
        }
        
        /* WhatsApp Pulse */
        .whatsapp-pulse {
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .whatsapp-pulse::before,
        .whatsapp-pulse::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -4px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #25D366;
            animation: pulse-ring 2s cubic-bezier(0.215, 0.61, 0.355, 1) infinite;
        }
        
        .whatsapp-pulse::after {
            animation-delay: 1s;
        }
        
        /* Voice Wave Animation */
        .voice-wave {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 3px;
            height: 30px;
        }
        
        .voice-bar {
            width: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--primary-blue), var(--neon-blue));
            border-radius: 2px;
            animation: wave 1s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        .voice-bar:nth-child(1) { height: 10px; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .voice-bar:nth-child(2) { height: 20px; animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .voice-bar:nth-child(3) { height: 15px; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .voice-bar:nth-child(4) { height: 25px; animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .voice-bar:nth-child(5) { height: 12px; animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        
        @keyframes wave {
            0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(0.5); }
            50% { transform: scaleY(1); }
        }
        
        /* News Ticker */
        .news-ticker {
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        
        .news-ticker-content {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: scroll 30s linear infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes scroll {
            0% { transform: translateX(100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
        }
        
        /* Login Modal */
        .modal-backdrop {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }
        
        /* Video Card */
        .video-card {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }
        
        .video-card img {
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }
        
        .video-card:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        .play-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .video-card:hover .play-btn {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
        }
        
        /* AI Tools Grid */
        .tool-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .tool-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--neon-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        
        /* Text to Speech Button */
        .tts-btn {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            z-index: 50;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--neon-blue));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .tts-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6);
        }
        
        /* Particle Effect */
        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--neon-blue);
            border-radius: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0;
        }
        
        /* Locked Content */
        .locked-overlay {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }
        
        /* Hero Image Mask */
        .hero-mask {
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-white">

    <!-- Background Video -->
    <div class="bg-video-container">
        <video class="bg-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
            <source src="https://assets.mixkit.co/videos/preview/mixkit-digital-animation-of-futuristic-devices-99786-large.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
    </div>
    <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-40 glass px-4 py-3 transition-all duration-300" id="navbar">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg glow-anim">
                    AI
                </div>
                <span class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-blue-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">පොඩ්ඩා</span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Desktop WhatsApp -->
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-4">
                <a href="https://wa.me/94762196055" target="_blank" class="whatsapp-pulse flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-500/20 border border-green-500 px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-green-500/30 transition-all">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-green-400 text-xl"></i>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-green-300">076 219 6055</span>
                </a>
                <button onclick="toggleLoginModal()" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/50 transition-all transform hover:scale-105" id="loginBtn">
                    Login / Register
                </button>
                <button onclick="logout()" class="hidden bg-red-500/80 px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-red-600 transition-all" id="logoutBtn">
                    Logout
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Mobile Menu Button -->
            <button class="md:hidden text-2xl" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Mobile Menu -->
    <div id="mobileMenu" class="fixed inset-0 z-30 bg-black/95 transform translate-x-full transition-transform duration-300 md:hidden">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full gap-8">
            <a href="https://wa.me/94762196055" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl text-green-400">
                <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
                <span>076 219 6055</span>
            </a>
            <button onclick="toggleLoginModal()" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-xl font-semibold">
                Login / Register
            </button>
            <button onclick="toggleMobileMenu()" class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-3xl">
                <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-mask">
            <img src="https://kommodo.ai/i/e7Nt6TfRfTNia96oAItX" alt="AI Podda Hero" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60">
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-blue-200 to-cyan-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-2xl opacity-0" id="heroTitle">
                AI පොඩ්ඩා
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-light text-blue-100 mb-8 opacity-0" id="heroSubtitle">
                Welcome To Ai පොඩ්ඩා
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 opacity-0" id="heroCta">
                <button onclick="scrollToSection('intro')" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/50 transition-all transform hover:scale-110 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                    Start Learning
                </button>
                <button onclick="scrollToSection('courses')" class="glass px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-video"></i>
                    View Courses
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-10 w-20 h-20 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-xl float-anim"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-cyan-500/20 rounded-full blur-xl float-anim" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Introduction Section with AI Voice -->
    <section id="intro" class="py-20 px-4 relative">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto glass rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                        <i class="fas fa-robot mr-3"></i>ආයුබෝවන්
                    </h2>
                    <button onclick="playIntroVoice()" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/50 transition-all group">
                        <div class="voice-wave" id="voiceWave">
                            <div class="voice-bar"></div>
                            <div class="voice-bar"></div>
                            <div class="voice-bar"></div>
                            <div class="voice-bar"></div>
                            <div class="voice-bar"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="font-semibold">Play Voice</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-volume-up group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-200 space-y-4" id="introText">
                    <p class="sinhala-text">හැමෝම ආදරයෙං පිලිගන්නවා Ai Podda වෙත මාත් එක්ක ලොකේ පුරා ඇවිදින්න වගේම Ai වලින් සුපිරිම විඩියෝ හදලා මුදල් උපයන්න පුලුවං විදිය මගෙන් ඉගෙන ගන්න පුලුවන් ඒවගේම ඔයාගෙ Business එකට Promotion එකට ගැලපෙන Creative ඇඩ් හදාගන්න ඔයාට අපගෙන් පුලුවන්.. Set වෙමු මම එක්ක</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-blue-300">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                    <span>Click the play button to hear the AI voice narration in Sinhala</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Social Media Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Follow Us On Social Media
            </h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@ai_podda2?_r=1&_t=ZS-94bLsF3g1w5" target="_blank" class="social-icon flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-black border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl text-white group-hover:border-white transition-all">
                        <i class="fab fa-tiktok"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white">TikTok</span>
                </a>

                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1CCptRphbm/" target="_blank" class="social-icon flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group" style="color: #1877F2;">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/50 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl text-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-600/30 transition-all">
                        <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                    </div>
